Package: mlame
Title: Estimate Average Marginal Effects for Machine Learning Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jonas", "Beste", email = "jonas.beste@iab.de", role = "aut"),
    person("Arne", "Bethmann", email = "bethmann@uni-mannheim.de", role =
        c("aut", "cre")))
URL: https://mlame.github.io
BugReports: https://github.com/umasds/mlame/issues
Description: An easy way to estimate average marginal effects (AME), predicted
    probabilities / values and similar quantities from different kinds of
    machine learning algorithms. Bootstrap estimates of standard errors,
    confidence intervals and p-values are also provided.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    rpart,
    ggplot2,
    randomForest
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
